description:
No story spoilers! In this video, we’ll show you the first major boss that Sam encounters in Death Stranding 2. While a big BT has already shown its ugly, ghostly face earlier in the game, the mysterious giant mech is Sam’s first truly larger-than-life challenge.

#IGN #Gaming #DeathStranding2
title: Death Stranding 2: First Major Boss Fight | PS5 Pro 4K 60FPS Gameplay

author: IGN
description:
Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle is coming to theatres September 12th!

It is the Taisho Period in Japan. Tanjiro, a kindhearted boy who sells charcoal for a living, finds his family slaughtered by a demon. To make matters worse, his younger sister Nezuko, the sole survivor, has been transformed into a demon herself.

Though devastated by this grim reality, Tanjiro resolves to become a “demon slayer” so that he can turn his sister back into a human, and kill the demon that massacred his family.

#IGN #DemonSlayer #Anime
title: Demon Slayer: Kimetsu no Yaiba Infinity Castle - Official Trailer (2025) English Subtitles

author: IGN
description:
SPOILERS AHEAD...

Death Stranding 2: On the Beach is Hideo Kojima's latest, brain-twisting adventure. To help make sense of the wild third act, check out our ending explained.

We go over it all, starting with how DS2 sets the scene after the ending of Death Stranding 1, to explaining who the Armed Red Attackers are that attack Fragile and Lou, how Sam Porter Bridges defeats APAS 4000, along with the death of both Higgs and Fragile, plus the BB-28/Lou/Tomorrow and Louise connection, the Neil, Sam and Lucy love triangle, and finally, whether or not there'll be a Death Stranding 3, thanks to that post-credit scene featuring Tomorrow/Louise dressed up as a porter.

#IGN #DeathStranding2 #Kojima
title: Death Stranding 2 Ending Explained

author: IGN
description:
In today's Entertainment Fix we list off every actor confirmed for Capcom’s new live Action Street Fighter. The movie is heading into production this August and is gearing up for a March 2026 release. Some of the announced cast include: Grammy-winning rapper 50 Cent, Minecraft and Aquaman star Jason Momoa, and more! 

Plus, rumors of who will play the next James Bond get louder as sources say Amazon MGM Studios has a few actors on the top of their list. Hint: one of these actors you may have seen many many times in the MCU. MGM Studios also recently announced Dune’s Denis Villenouve as the new director and help start a post Daniel Craig era of Bond films — Presented by Universal Orlando Resort.
title: Every Street Fighter Character Confirmed For The Movie So Far | IGN The Fix: Entertainment

description:
Struggling to survive the climb in PEAK? This guide breaks down everything you need to know about the hunger system, including how it affects your stamina, what foods to eat (and avoid), and how to cook without poisoning yourself. From foraged berries and mushrooms to airplane meals and mysterious “Cure All” items, we’ll help you figure out what’s worth eating and what might send you tumbling back to the bottom.

#IGN #Gaming
title: PEAK Hunger Guide: Best Foods, Poison Risks, and How to Survive the Climb
